{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block body_classes -%}
  index
{%- endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <h1>Only {{ daysLeft }} days until <a href="/groundhog-day-2023" class="underline">Groundhog Day 2023</a>.</h1>

  <aside class="intro-sentence">
    <div>
      <span><a href="/about" class="underline">Groundhog Day</a> is a North American holiday where groundhogs predict the arrival of spring.</span>
      <span><a href="#index--about">{{ site_title() }}</a> lists <a href="#index--groundhogs" class="underline">prognosticating groundhogs</a> and their <a href="#index--predictions" class="underline">yearly predictions</a>.</span>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <div class="heading-with-right-link">
    <h2 class="heading h3" id="index--predictions"><a href="/predictions">Predictions by year</a></h2>
    <div class="right-link"><a href="/groundhog-day-2023" class="link--icon link--icon--right">
      <span>2023</span> {{ icon({ right: true }) }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>The yearly result is what the majority of groundhogs agreed on.</p>
  <ul class="card--grid no-paragraph-margin">
    {% for result in predictionResults %}
      <li>
        <a href="/predictions/{{ result.year }}">
          <div class="card card--{{ result.prediction }}">
            <span class="card--triangle"></span>
            <div class="card--heading h2">{{ result.year }}</div>
            {% if result.prediction == 'winter' %}
              <div class="card--subhead"><span aria-hidden="true">‚ùÑÔ∏è</span> Longer winter</div>
            {% else %}
              <div class="card--subhead"><span aria-hidden="true">üåº</span> Early spring</div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="card--details card--bg-change">{{ result.groundhogs[result.agree] }} groundhogs agreed, {{ result.groundhogs[result.disagree] }} did not</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
    <a href="/predictions" class="link--icon link--icon--right underline">
      <span>All years</span> {{ icon({ right: true }) }}
    </a>
  </div>

  <br />
  <div class="heading-with-right-link">
    <h2 class="heading h3" id="index--groundhogs"><a href="/groundhogs">Groundhogs</a></h2>
    <div class="right-link">
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>These are 3 randomly-selected prognosticators out of <a href="/groundhogs"><strong>{{ totalGroundhogs }}</strong> total groundhogs</a>.</p>

  <ul class="card--grid no-paragraph-margin">
    {% for groundhog in randomGroundhogs %}
      <li>
        <a href="/groundhogs/{{ groundhog.slug }}">
          {% set class = 'card--winter' if groundhog.shadow else 'card--spring' %}
          {% set latestPrediction = 'longer winter' if groundhog.shadow else 'early spring' %}
          <div class="card {{ class }}">
            <span class="card--triangle"></span>
            <div class="card--heading h5">{{ groundhog.name }}</div>
            <div class="card--subhead">{{ groundhog.location }}</div>
            <div class="card--details card--bg-change">Latest prediction: {{ latestPrediction }}</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
    <a href="/groundhogs" class="link--icon link--icon--right underline">
      <span>All groundhogs</span> {{ icon({ right: true }) }}
    </a>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top: .5rem;">
    or, explore the
    <a class="link--icon underline" href="/map">
      {{ icon({ map: true }) }} <span>Groundhog Map</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <br />

  <h2 class="h4" id="index--about">About GROUNDHOG-DAY.com</h2>
  <div class="max-width--850">
    <p>{{ site_title() }} is the leading data source for North America‚Äôs prophetic prognosticators: unleashing the ancient wisdom of <a href="/groundhogs">groundhogs</a> with the entrepreneurial dynamism of <a href="/api">structured data</a>.</p>
    <p>Every February 2nd ‚Äì in deepest, darkest winter ‚Äì humanity seeks guidance from mystic marmots, whose obscure rituals and ancient tongue foretell of spring‚Äôs return. <a href="/history-of-groundhog-day">The tradition is fascinating</a>, but the future is now.</p>
    <p class="mb--0">Move over, ‚Äòunicorn‚Äô companies ‚Äî we‚Äôve got our own magic animal.</p>
  </div>

{% endblock %}
